<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>{{title}} - {{projects.svg-plotter.name}}</title>
  {{> head}}
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    {{> header}}
    <div class="card">
      <header class="card__header">
        <h2 class="font-medium text-xl">{{projects.trash-panda.name}}</h2>
      </header>
      <p>Trash Panda was built to streamline the experience of responsible waste disposal.<p>
      <p>Users take a photo of their waste or search for a match. Depending on the item, they may be asked some simple follow-up questions to help improve the disposal suggestion. Finally, they are presented with a clear recommendation along with local alternatives for waste-diversion when available.</p>
      <p>The system was design to be customized for each municipality with a comprehensive management system. This system included a unique diagramming tool for defining the rules for a given municipality.<p>
      <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-3">Gallery</h3>
      <div class="gallery">
        {{#projects.trash-panda.gallery}}
        <a class="button button--image" href="{{.}}">
          <div class="button__paddle">
            <img class="button__image" src="{{.}}" />
          </div>
        </a>
        {{/projects.trash-panda.gallery}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
